{"tid":1831253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】假如有人捉鬼, 我會做左膠！鬼會自己浮上水, 唔洗捉嘅！","createTime":"2020-01-20T09:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:34.000Z","uid":167548,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"819ac3f985bbab90b956709a27c23bf869cd20ee","tid":1831253,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"提早講定先, 驚有心人煸動or令真勇武上當, 出神獸誤傷自己人。<br />\n<br />\n鬼是會自己浮上水！再私了佢老味！<br />\n琴日真是好撚柒隻狗, 自己自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現場班糾察/記者再用身擋, 後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等班狗自爆就Okay㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔捉鬼, 一樣保持<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警惕</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申遮打現場(發夢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提防極端化, 假如有一隊卧底狗突然指控某人是狗, 就會再出事炒大車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">何為阻膠, 罪證確鑿下包庇敵軍, 以身抵擋！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"08bffb29dabf0bb83a59eed2fcb09ac23e591c6e","tid":1831253,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"提防警狗派人亂咁指控(極端化), 再私了, <br />\n阻止「捉師天師」唔是阻膠。<br />\n最想我地捉鬼嘅得警狗。"},{"pid":"1a53a1d1e97ba80cc4032829802524a40eacc751","tid":1831253,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"阻止捉鬼嘅人唔是阻膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"ff9734b59efd5c924aa480f1bd1ea25b3f865eb5","tid":1831253,"uid":16